{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2959111, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你说的这些我都知道，我也相信同学确实缺钱。但是这并不代表怀疑是不应当的。有疑点就该怀疑。要是一万个里面有一个真有没有那么急需缺但号召捐款的，都是对同学们的捐款积极性的打击，会让后来的真正需要帮助的同学得不到帮助。", "timestamp": 1637078689, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959119, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": 2959111, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 一万个里面有一个是不会打击大家的。这不是狼来了的世界。", "timestamp": 1637078733, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959133, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": 2959111, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 可能会打击到你？可是成年人的世界就是错误和容错的。想让人认错，不很现实。", "timestamp": 1637078767, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959136, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大家有疑问，并不是要攻击那位同学的家人，而是希望听到解释、确保自己的钱真的被用于救命，而非被用于维持生活质量。这也是号召捐款方应该做的。", "timestamp": 1637078783, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959148, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": 2959133, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 既然可能错误，为什么这个“错误可能性”要我自己吞下去呢？为什么我不应该去确认有没有错误呢？", "timestamp": 1637078814, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": 2959136, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 因为现在没有人【有义务】解释，正如平台设置可以隐藏资产情况一样，这不是必须公开的。懂了吗？", "timestamp": 1637078929, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959199, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": 2959148, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你可以去确认，但是没有人会回答你。你明白吗？", "timestamp": 1637078951, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959210, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": 2959136, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: “这也是号召捐款方应该做的。”不好意思，这不是。", "timestamp": 1637078987, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959417, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": 2959191, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 自然是有义务的。隐瞒经济情况，就得有被怀疑的心理准备。要想让大家相信并捐款，就有义务公开说明。我认为这是一个基本共识", "timestamp": 1637079526, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959506, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": 2959417, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你最大的问题就是书读的太少而想得太多。", "timestamp": 1637079773, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959520, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": 2959417, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: “自然”“是有”“就得有”“就有”“我认为”。你的话中，自我意识过剩了。", "timestamp": 1637079817, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2959905, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561654, "reply_to": 2959520, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你明白了吗？懂了吗？爹味太浓了吧", "timestamp": 1637081289, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 561654, "reply": 12, "tag": null, "text": "#561579", "timestamp": 1637078227, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637081291, "url": "", "vote": {}}}